				<A href="/geography/default.asp?MAPID=1417">Northern Ro</a><br>
				
				<A href="/geography/default.asp?MAPID=1616">Oasis of Marr</a><br>
				
				</font>
				<br><br>
				<font face="verdana" size="3">
				<p><b>Faction Hits:</b></font>
				<font face="verdana" size="2">
				<u><b>Worse</b></u><br></font>
				<font face="verdana" size="1">
				None<br>
				</font>
				<br>
				<font face="verdana" size="2">
				<u><b>Better</b></u><br></font><font face="verdana" size="1">
				None<br>
				</font>
				<br>
				</p></td>
		  </tr>
		  <tr>
		    <td colspan="3" width="100%" align="center">
		    <font face="verdana" size="2">These are not that difficult, until you run across one that throws magic at you.  They hit fairly hard with their spells, and (known from experience here) their spells will take down a level 14 wizard in about three hits.  Loot is usually water or rations.</font></td>
		  </tr>
		  <tr>
		    <td colspan="3" width="100%">
		    <font face="verdana" size="2">Submitted by: <A href="mailto:">Ipsidack</a></font></td>
		  </tr>
